          <text><![CDATA[<p>Expresses the sense of the Senate that:</p> <ul> <li>climate change is real and human activity is the main driver of it;</li> <li>it is in the public interest that broadcast meteorologists knowledgeably communicate scientifically-based climate information; and</li> <li>fossil fuel companies, public-relations firms, and foundations should cease their misinformation campaigns concerning the dangers of climate change.<br /></li></ul>]]></text>
